    public abstract class ExprTreeSpecies
extends net.sf.jclec.exprtree.ExprTreeSpecies
    ExprTreeSpecies for ExprTreeClassificationRules.

    Extends the ExprTreeSpecies for classification problems in order to provide dataset metadata to generate the appropriate rules.

    Author:
    Amelia Zafra, Sebastian Ventura, Jose M. Luna, Alberto Cano, Juan Luis Olmo
